    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Trailer Park Zombies</strong> 是一款混乱的生存 Roguelite / survivors-like FPS，充满了无尽的僵尸浪潮、丰富的武器选择和紧张刺激的动作！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104850/extras/21d469552aafc0d7c8c84c7c93638a6a.poster.avif?t=1767914633\" width=1168 height=492 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104850/extras/21d469552aafc0d7c8c84c7c93638a6a.webm?t=1767914633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从多个乡巴佬角色中选择，并在生存之战中对抗被僵尸化的比利（Billies）和凯伦（Karens）大军。每个可玩角色都有不同的特性，帮助你更长时间生存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104850/extras/896ff19614060009c558d30f8cdfaa6b.poster.avif?t=1767914633\" width=1168 height=492 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104850/extras/896ff19614060009c558d30f8cdfaa6b.webm?t=1767914633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主要特色 </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无尽的僵尸浪潮</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >R随机生成地图</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着进度解锁新角色和武器</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可破坏的环境</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鸡</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >90年代复古射击游戏风格</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104850/extras/66f1e6128e7168623dcc866d9f9c8536.poster.avif?t=1767914633\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104850/extras/66f1e6128e7168623dcc866d9f9c8536.webm?t=1767914633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
